Package pdqninja.pdq

Interface Summary
Adder<E> Adds two objects.
Mergeable A class implements the Mergeable interface to indicate that its complete form can be constructed from smaller instances.
Splittable A class implements the Splittable interface to indicate that it can be divided into smaller instances.
 

Class Summary
PDQ Access to the
PDQConfig Configurations for the PDQ environment.
PDQWorker Daemon process that runs on slave machines and performs computation on behalf of a master.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Parallel Indicates that the method is intended to be executed by the PDQ library (via the PDQ.run() methods).
Shared Indicates that the argument will be shared across the multiple parallel or distributed instantiations of the computation.
